    "date": "2023-09-19T10:42:14Z",
    "text": "Reducing Exposure to Burn Pits Act\n\nThis bill requires the Office of the Under Secretary of Defense for Acquisition and Sustainment within the Department of Defense to submit a report to Congress on incinerators and waste-to-energy waste disposal alternatives to burn pits (areas used for burning solid waste in open air without equipment). The report must be submitted not later than 60 days after the President submits the budget for FY2025."
